{"tid":317904,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[紅磚特產]JS3492 BA(HONS)SCHEME IN FASHION&TEXTILES有問必答區","createTime":"2017-07-11T18:25:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T17:09:14.000Z","uid":128105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b22feb7cc0ed80bc83dd515057cc1e2a4b754d00","tid":317904,"uid":128105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:25:00.000Z","msg":"過多幾個鐘就放榜<br />\n唔知各位巴絲緊唔緊張呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相信大家都有聽過POLYU FASHION呢科<br />\n話哂都係八大入面poly獨有<br />\n想讀既人肯定唔小<br />\n而家就開個集中討論post黎答各位未來fm既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n常見問題Q&amp;A<br />\n<br />\n1.呢科係讀咩？<br />\n<br />\n其實ITC有分唔同Major，分別係Fashion design，IA design內衣設計，Knitwear design，Fashion retailing，Fashion marketing同Fashion technology <br />\nYear1個陣，所有fm讀既科都係一樣，去到year2既sem2先會分stream讀<br />\n所以大家可以係yr1既時候報讀唔同既course，去選擇自己心儀既major<br />\n<br />\n2.幾分先入到？<br />\n16年dse就22分穩入 中英有8就得<br />\n21-19分都可以透過interview入<br />\n17dse應該會降到21-20分就入得<br />\n<br />\n3.係咪水泡科？<br />\nTo be honest，對呢科冇興趣但dse分高不成低不就，佢係科好既水泡<br />\n但你係有心讀fashion，想做呢行既，就係你不二之選<br />\n<br />\n講住咁多先<br />\n有問題歡迎下面留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba55dadbb3a0aeb626c7615d872a4a93bbd27738","tid":317904,"uid":128105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:31:52.000Z","msg":"推比同學仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62b7647fe22cedb47bec657342bf277dfd4e345","tid":317904,"uid":102463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:36:29.000Z","msg":"想入Hd 如果英文2左會唔會好難入？"},{"pid":"92b51bae5650d38f854fb3a0f6219dea231639bf","tid":3179